        "remove_horizontal_spacing": false,
        "liquid": "<div class=\"elixara-clean-box\">\n\n  <div class=\"elixara-top-trust\">\n    <div>✓ Free Shipping</div>\n    <div>↺ 30-Day Guarantee</div>\n    <div>🌱 Vegan Formula</div>\n    <div>🔒 Secure Checkout</div>\n  </div>\n\n  <p class=\"elixara-kicker\">ADVANCED HAIR GROWTH CARE</p>\n\n  <h2>Stronger roots, visibly fuller-looking hair.</h2>\n\n  <p class=\"elixara-desc\">\n    Elixara helps support weaker hair, nourish the scalp, and promote a healthier-looking hair growth routine over time.\n  </p>\n\n  <div class=\"elixara-benefits-list\">\n\n    <div>\n      <strong>Strengthens Roots</strong>\n      <span>Supports healthier and stronger hair from the scalp.</span>\n    </div>\n\n    <div>\n      <strong>Helps Reduce Hair Fall</strong>\n      <span>Perfect for stress-related shedding, post-partum hair loss, or thinning hair.</span>\n    </div>\n\n    <div>\n      <strong>Supports Hair Growth</strong>\n      <span>For hair that looks fuller, denser, and healthier.</span>\n    </div>\n\n    <div>\n      <strong>Nourishes The Scalp</strong>\n      <span>Provides comfort and care for dry or weakened scalps.</span>\n    </div>\n\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"elixara-ingredients\">\n\n    <strong>Gentle & Vegan Formula</strong>\n\n    <p>\n      Made with plant-based extracts, silicone-free, paraben-free, and designed for daily use.\n    </p>\n\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"elixara-mini-result\">\n    Recommended routine: 90 to 150 days for progressive visible results.\n  </div>\n\n</div>\n\n<section class=\"elixara-faq\">\n\n  <div class=\"faq-title\">\n\n    <p>FREQUENTLY ASKED QUESTIONS</p>\n\n    <h2>\n      Everything you need to know about<br>\n      <span>Elixara</span>\n    </h2>\n\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"faq-container\">\n\n    <details class=\"faq-item\" open>\n\n      <summary>When will I start seeing results?</summary>\n\n      <p>\n        Results may vary depending on the individual. With consistent use, most users begin noticing visible improvements within 4 to 6 weeks.\n      </p>\n\n    </details>\n\n    <details class=\"faq-item\">\n\n      <summary>How do I use Elixara?</summary>\n\n      <p>\n        Apply a few drops directly onto the scalp and gently massage for 1–2 minutes. Do not rinse.\n      </p>\n\n    </details>\n\n    <details class=\"faq-item\">\n\n      <summary>How long should I use it?</summary>\n\n      <p>\n        For best results, we recommend using Elixara consistently for 90 to 150 days.\n      </p>\n\n    </details>\n\n    <details class=\"faq-item\">\n\n      <summary>Who is Elixara for?</summary>\n\n      <p>\n        Elixara is suitable for both men and women experiencing thinning, weak, fragile, or shedding hair.\n      </p>\n\n    </details>\n\n    <details class=\"faq-item\">\n\n      <summary>Can I use it after pregnancy or during stressful periods?</summary>\n\n      <p>\n        Yes. Elixara can be added to a hair care routine during post-partum shedding, stress-related hair fall, or seasonal changes.\n      </p>\n\n    </details>\n\n    <details class=\"faq-item\">\n\n      <summary>Is the formula natural?</summary>\n\n      <p>\n        The formula is made with plant-based extracts, is vegan, silicone-free, and paraben-free.\n      </p>\n\n    </details>\n\n    <details class=\"faq-item\">\n\n      <summary>Is shipping free?</summary>\n\n      <p>\n        Yes, we currently offer free shipping today.\n      </p>\n\n    </details>\n\n    <details class=\"faq-item\">\n\n      <summary>Do you offer a guarantee?</summary>\n\n      <p>\n        Yes, every order is backed by our 30-Day Money Back Guarantee.\n      </p>\n\n    </details>\n\n  </div>\n\n</section>\n\n<style>\n\n.elixara-clean-box{\n  background:#FFFFFF;\n  border:1px solid rgba(2,153,66,.16);\n  border-radius:24px;\n  padding:18px;\n  margin-top:-28px;\n  margin-bottom:18px;\n  box-shadow:0 8px 24px rgba(0,0,0,.05);\n}\n\n.elixara-top-trust{\n  display:grid;\n  grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr);\n  gap:8px